Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.16,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あっ　ただいま\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}啊　我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.01,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただいま\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.64,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おかえり\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.51,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ん\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}嗯
