Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.92,0:48:56.43,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}みんないつもどおりだ\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}大家都和平時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.12,0:48:58.33,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ビューティフォーディ\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.62,0:49:01.66,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつもどおり\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}和平時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.04,0:49:06.97,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつも\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}平時
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.47,0:49:09.40,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たまこ　おはよう\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}玉子　早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.40,0:49:56.65,JPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いち　に　さん\N{\fs9} \N{\fs24}{\rCHN\blur3}一　二　三
